dcterms:creator: Xun Gong
Nathan W. Hill
dcterms:description: The Burmish dataset consists of 8 Burmish languages, and 269 etymologies that are reflected in at least two descendant languages with a total of 1,442 reflexes.
dcterms:title: Burmish Dataset

dcterms:creator: Theraphan Luangthongkum
dcterms:description: The Karen dataset consists of 10 Karenic languages, and offers 365 etymologies originally proposed by Luangthongkum, which are reflected in at least 2 languages with a total of 2,866 reflexes.
dcterms:title: Karen Dataset

dcterms:creator: Sanderson Castro Soares de Oliveira
dcterms:description: The Panoan dataset consists of 20 Panoan languages, and includes the reconstruction of 514 cognate sets across 470 concepts proposed by Oliveira. In total, the dataset features 7,305 reflexes.
dcterms:title: Panoan Dataset
